Package resource

resource contains web service resource classes for the ComPosting API
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MaterialsV1
    Root resource for Material classes, providing GET method handling for the return of result lists via the Response object.
    MaterialsV2
    Root resource for Material classes, providing GET method handling for the return of individual results via the Response object.
    MaterialsV3
    Root resource for Material classes, providing POST method handling for creation of new records.
    PeriodsV1
    Root resource for Period classes, providing GET method handling for the return of result lists via the Response object.
    PeriodsV2
    Root resource for Period classes, providing GET method handling for the return of individual results via the Response object.
    PeriodsV3
    Root resource for Period classes, providing POST method handling for creation of new records.
    PricesV1
    Root resource for Price classes, providing GET method handling for the return of result lists via the Response object.
    PricesV2
    Root resource for Price classes, providing GET method handling for the return of individual results via the Response object.
    PricesV3
    Root resource for Price classes, providing POST method handling for creation of new records.
    ServicesV1
    Root resource for Service classes, providing GET method handling for the return of result lists via the Response object.
    ServicesV2
    Root resource for Service classes, providing GET method handling for the return of individual results via the Response object.
    ServicesV3
    Root resource for Service classes, providing POST method handling for creation of new records.
